   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Chronic Fatigue Syndrome</h3> 
    <p>Chronic fatigue syndrome, or CFS, causes you to feel so tired that you canâ€™t complete normal, daily activities. While chronic fatigue syndrome has no known cause and is difficult to diagnose, its major symptoms can be treated. </p> 
